---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Me | Attachment Matters, LLC" 
    description="Meet a highly experienced, compassionate LCSW dedicated to attachment-focused, trauma-responsive clinical work.">
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <!-- IMPORTANT: Replace this src with the path to your actual headshot image -->
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x700.png/EAE5DC/333333?text=Your+Professional+Headshot" alt="Headshot of the therapist" class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-charcoal">Warm, Compassionate, and Uncompromisingly Skilled</h1>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-brand-charcoal/80">
                        I am a client-centered provider who combines deep compassion with exceptional skill. With **16 years of experience** in complex family systems, I have earned a reputation as a leading professional in the region for a reason: I am dedicated to achieving positive outcomes for the families I serve.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-brand-charcoal/80">
                        As an LCSW for 14 years with a spotless ethical record, my approach is always relationship-driven, attachment-focused, and trauma-responsive.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-24 bg-white/70 p-10 rounded-2xl border border-brand-stone/80">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-center">My Integrative & Evidence-Based Approach</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-brand-charcoal/80 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    I utilize a wide array of evidence-based practices to support your family's unique journey to bonding and wellness.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Cognitive Behavior Therapy (CBT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Child Centered Play Therapy</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Synergetic Play Therapy (SPT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Parent Child Interactional Therapy (PCIT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">The Neurosequential Model</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-stone text-brand-charcoal/80 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Trauma Focused CBT (TF-CBT)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>